Class Search

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • master.Search
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public class Search
extends java.lang.Thread
    Search will perform Scanning once the robot finishes Localizing to (0,0) Once a block is captured, it will move to the right zone to drop the block and come back to the starting corner.
    Since:
    2016-11-28
    Version:
    2.0
    Author:
    Yu-Yueh Liu, Jerome Marfleet
